title: Ep. 1240 - Haathi Is Stuck Under The Tree - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha calls Taarak and asks him to reach to the spot immediately. Haathi explains the crowd about him being stuck under the tree. Goli calls his Chacha for help.

title: Ep. 1241 - Gokuldham To The Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone tries their best to help Haathi. Sodhi tries to lift the branch under which Haathi is stuck. Haathi suffers from severe back pain. Popatlal gets a call from a girl for marriage proposal.

title: Ep. 1242 - Haathis's Brothers To The Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Haathi's brothers lift the branches but Haathi couldn't move. Gokuldham society together decide to help the brothers to get Haathi out. Babita comes up with an idea.

title: Ep. 1243 - Babita's Plan Fails - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi hits the vegetable stall and everyone starts picking up the vegetables. Nattu kaka comes with an axe to cut down the tree and help Haathi come out. Ladies of a campaign thinks Popatlal has cut the tree and warns them not to do such things.

title: Ep. 1244 - Military Helps Haathi - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya explains the situation to the military. Finally with their help, Haathi manages to come out. Everyone asks Haathi to go home first but he is unable to get up and complains about the severe ache in his back.

title: Ep. 1245 - Champaklal Shouts At Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal gets a call, Champaklal thinks it to be the fire brigade. Chacha Ji shouts at Popatlal and asks him to tell the fire brigade that they are no longer needed. Upon asking, Poptalal reveals that an alliance is coming to meet him in the evening.

title: Ep. 1246 - Case Against Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police arrests Popatlal and everyone is in a shock. Abdul tells everyone that the campaign lady has filed a case against Popatlal for cutting down the tree. Popatlal tries to defend himself but of no use.

title: Ep. 1247 - Haathi Gives His Statement - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Haathi explains the police as how the tree fell and he was stuck beneath that. Police asks them if they have any proof of Popatlal being innocent. Iyer finds a chemical for which the roots were weak and the tree fell.

title: Ep. 1248 - Daya Is Excited For Navratri Utsav - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha and Daya plan to make the Navratri Utsav special. Komal suggests everyone to try something different this time. Daya asks everyone if this could be celebrated the traditional way and everyone agrees to it.

title: Ep. 1249 - Bhide Takes The Responsibility - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is in charge of the drummers. He calls and books them for the event and informs Madhavi about the same. Popatlal worries as he doesn't have the traditional dress but Bhide tells him that Daya will take care of it.

title: Ep. 1250 - Abdul Has A Solution - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Abdul says Sodhi has a Dhol. Popatlal promises to get the drummers and make the event as Daya had wanted it to. Everyone is restless but Daya defends Popatlal and asks to wait a little more. Finally the drummers arrive.

title: Ep. 1251 - Bollywood's Action Hero In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Akshay Kumar joins Gokuldham for the event. Daya requests Akshay to play Garba with them before he leaves. Akshay asks everyone to blindfold themselves and then dance. Later, he is nowhere to be found.

title: Ep. 1252 - Tapu Sena Missing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is worried as Sonu has still not reached home. Madhvi asks him not to worry much and let it be. Bhide meets Champaklal and asks him if he knows where the kids are but Chacha Ji asks him the same. Finally, they are found in the clubhouse.

title: Ep. 1253 - What About The Money? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu calls Bhide to know if they have found who had lost the money. Tapu asks for proof then he will hand over the money. Tapu Sena along with Champaklal, Bhide, and Popatlal looks for the real owner.

title: Ep. 1254 - A Big Mistake - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After money being deposited in the donation box of a temple, Champaklal, Bhide, Popatlal and Tapu Sena finds the person who had lost the money. Chacha ji assures him that he will arrange the money.
